## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available online resources and may not encompass all aspects of the impact of abusive parenting on child development. The data is limited to the scope of the studies and articles reviewed, and there may be additional factors and nuances not covered in this report. Further research, particularly longitudinal studies, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the long-term effects of abusive parenting.